window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>There’s trouble in the borderlands, and I’m the only one that can stop it.</b></p> <p>I’ve done my best to rebuild my home in the little town of West Hollow, settling down with Serena and Lynnette. We’re already starting to feel like a family, but just when things feel too good to be true, trouble arises in the forms of a vengeful war wizard and a pompous duke.</p> <p>To stop them, I’m going to have to ally with a gorgeous witch who still wants me dead, even if that means breaking with the kingdom and carving our own path.</p> <p><b>A man has to make his own way. This one is mine.</b></p>"; 
